Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-mistralai`, instrumenting the `mistralai`
v1 Python SDK chat completions (`chat.complete` / `chat.complete_async`,
`chat.stream` / `chat.stream_async`) and embeddings (`embeddings.create` /
`embeddings.create_async`), emitting standard GenAI semantic conventions
(`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
